---
// Forces dark mode site-wide (the terminal-themed palette is dark-only by
// design). Replaces Starlight's ThemeProvider, which reads localStorage and
// the system preference; paired with an empty ThemeSelect override so the
// light/dark toggle never renders.
---

{/* Inlined to avoid a flash of the wrong theme before hydration. */}
<script is:inline>
  document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'dark';
</script>
